verbose_text: As shown in Figures XREF_FIG C, D, the anti-IL-23 antibody did not significantly alter SAA3 induced IL-22 production in neutrophils but inhibited IL-22 production by mouse splenocytes that were used as a control for effective inhibition by the anti-IL-23.
evidence: anti-IL-23 antibody did not significantly alter SAA3-induced IL-22 production in neutrophils but inhibited IL-22
